#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.10"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.10:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.10:0.2"
msgid "1. Bālavagga"
msgstr "1. Fools"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.10:0.3"
msgid "10. Malasutta"
msgstr "10. Stains"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.10:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato tayo male appahāya yathābhataṃ "
"nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr ""
"“Anyone who has three qualities, and has not given up three stains, is cast "
"down to hell."

msgctxt "an3.10:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.10:1.3"
msgid "Dussīlo ca hoti, dussīlyamalañcassa appahīnaṃ hoti;"
msgstr "They’re unethical, and haven’t given up the stain of immorality."

msgctxt "an3.10:1.4"
msgid "issukī ca hoti, issāmalañcassa appahīnaṃ hoti;"
msgstr "They’re envious, and haven’t given up the stain of envy."

msgctxt "an3.10:1.5"
msgid "maccharī ca hoti, maccheramalañcassa appahīnaṃ hoti."
msgstr "They’re stingy, and haven’t given up the stain of stinginess."

msgctxt "an3.10:1.6"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato ime tayo male appahāya "
"yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ niraye."
msgstr ""
"Anyone who has these three qualities, and has not given up these three "
"stains, is cast down to hell."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.10:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tīhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato tayo male pahāya yathābhataṃ nikkhitto "
"evaṃ sagge."
msgstr ""
"Anyone who has three qualities, and has given up three stains, is raised up "
"to heaven."

msgctxt "an3.10:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi tīhi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.10:2.3"
msgid "Sīlavā ca hoti, dussīlyamalañcassa pahīnaṃ hoti;"
msgstr "They’re ethical, and have given up the stain of immorality."

msgctxt "an3.10:2.4"
msgid "anissukī ca hoti, issāmalañcassa pahīnaṃ hoti;"
msgstr "They’re not envious, and have given up the stain of envy."

msgctxt "an3.10:2.5"
msgid "amaccharī ca hoti, maccheramalañcassa pahīnaṃ hoti."
msgstr "They’re not stingy, and have given up the stain of stinginess."

msgctxt "an3.10:2.6"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, tīhi dhammehi samannāgato ime tayo male pahāya "
"yathābhataṃ nikkhitto evaṃ sagge”ti."
msgstr ""
"Anyone who has these three qualities, and has given up these three stains, "
"is raised up to heaven.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.10:2.7"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.10:2.8"
msgid "Bālavaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.10:3.1"
msgid "Bhayaṃ lakkhaṇacintī ca,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.10:3.2"
msgid "accayañca ayoniso;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.10:3.3"
msgid "Akusalañca sāvajjaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.10:3.4"
msgid "sabyābajjhakhataṃ malanti."
msgstr ""
